text.tspan: FIGURE 2 Crude Sandwich and Grandsandwich Index (1970 cohort).
NOTE: The Crude Index is the populationweighted sum of agespecific probabilities of (grand)sandwichness.
The maps show mean values for men and women combined.

tspan.tspan: The Crude Sandwich Index for Guatemalans born in 1970 is 4.2
